  - The new Project object is stored in the system.
  - A new ActivityEntry object is created.
  - The ActivityEntry is associated with the Project.
  - The ActivityEntry's attributes (timestamp and description) are set to indicate that the project was created.

Postcondition (Failure Scenario):
