  - There is no ActivityEntry object created.
  - The system state remains unchanged.

Postcondition (Failure Scenario when keyword is invalid):
  - There is a Task object with the given taskId in the system.
  - The tag keyword is invalid.
  - There is no tag created or associated.
  - There is no ActivityEntry object created.
  - The system state remains unchanged.


